","msg":"L冇&ldquo;奴&rdquo;音<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n此post已完<br />\n<br />\n/'&epsilon;l/"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T11:52:19.000Z","msg":"L真係無『奴』音，你可以將/'&epsilon;l/擺入IPA Reader聽下，我口中平時啲人讀嘅『L奴』係/&epsilon;ləʊ/，你可以比較下有咩分別。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T11:54:38.000Z","msg":"咁h都係一樣你講到有分別咁<br />\n都係consonant後面加多左vowel"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T12:02:02.000Z","msg":"可能我講得唔清楚，H同L個case嘅分別在於H變ait廚係有幫助到母語係粵語嘅人發/ʃ/，而/&epsilon;ləʊ/對發/'&epsilon;l/無幫助，所以我覺得H係合理演化，而L唔係。               <br />\n<br />\n  btw,多謝你肯同我討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e74415e2878ecdf7a543760fcacf2ce8f6e6684","tid":2454537,"uid":158886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T12:46:20.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba2d22fbc9013e48ad66b1f2b7786a17169c5498","tid":2454537,"uid":81424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T12:47:35.000Z","msg":"w 同 v 唔係口音問題<br />\n係直頭讀錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e55631a05309c4aed3991a28a21c692a3b28ab6","tid":2454537,"uid":158886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ba2d22fbc9013e48ad66b1f2b7786a17169c5498","tid":2454537,"uid":81424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T12:47:35.000Z","msg":"w 同 v 唔係口音問題<br />\n係直頭讀錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T13:23:48.000Z","msg":"嚴格黎講所有同字典唔同嘅讀音都係讀錯，我覺得呢樣野可以分幾部分思考。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/read.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n首先係一個人讀錯一個字嘅原因係咩，有可能係環境因素(例如身邊無人讀得正確，老師教得唔好，etc.)；亦可能係個人因素(自己無心機學/讀，受母語影響，先天缺陷例如痴脷筋，etc.)<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其次就係邊類型嘅『錯誤』應該改『正』呢？我呢個post主要就係想討論呢一點。 我自己嘅邏輯係，喺唔係英語作母語嘅前提下，只要個『錯誤』係因為母語嘅限制而造成，咁就屬於口音嘅範圍入面。咁係咪受母語限制就唔洗改，唔洗進步呢？ 當然唔係啦，簡單講就係佢睇錯得幾有道理或者幾無道理，黎作出相應嘅批評。好似W同V呢啲受母語限制所造成嘅錯誤雖然較值得原諒，但都應該盡量改善。而L奴R奴呢啲就抵比人批評。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n簡單講我嘅立場係我覺得同一種語言嘅使用者應該盡量令自己講出黎嘅野同其他人一樣，咁樣會容易溝通好多，但係我地亦無需要因為有唔同而感到自卑。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"831a65f643914ac54b77a98d6d6a4386e37546df","tid":2454537,"uid":281306,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T13:27:19.000Z","msg":"是<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聽燒縮縮學到唔少野<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcad6d006b38157c6442c5cc1dce8d4f280b3e3e","tid":2454537,"uid":18772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T13:36:34.000Z","msg":"咁利物薄口音係咪你所講既野"},{"pid":"042c7421a27b600d7ef57425463177f9382b4fc4","tid":2454537,"uid":158886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bcad6d006b38157c6442c5cc1dce8d4f280b3e3e","tid":2454537,"uid":18772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T13:36:34.000Z","msg":"咁利物薄口音係咪你所講既野"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T13:48:35.000Z","msg":"我講緊嘅係母語唔係英文嘅口音，例如香港口音嘅英文、法國口音嘅英文，所以唔係。 而且我對Scouse呢類地區口音認識唔深，所以無拎出黎討論。我淨係知Scouse受Irish嘅影響好深，但再深入啲我就唔清楚了。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c18648b74c8f41dd42d0873587589696e1490905","tid":2454537,"uid":24457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T13:50:03.000Z","msg":"口音=無錯<br />\n讀錯=約定俗成=無錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"621c708f64187a2780cbcf16bbc79004c9280c52","tid":2454537,"uid":143305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T13:51:53.000Z","msg":"咁f同v點分"},{"pid":"1e347ab19ef06ed083aade332a7cd010b6216dad","tid":2454537,"uid":158886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c18648b74c8f41dd42d0873587589696e1490905","tid":2454537,"uid":24457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"rep